  "title": "SENATE RESOLUTION CREATING A SPECIAL LEGISLATIVE COMMISSION TO STUDY AND PROVIDE RECOMMENDATIONS FOR JUVENILE HEARING BOARDS",
  "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"upper\"}",
  "classification": [
